disclaimerForm: The data collected is intended for use by the company autobiz SAS, data controller, for the services provided on its autobizTrade website, a B2B marketplace (creation of an authenticated user profile, customer relation management, sales promotion, reporting), as well as for the purposes of sales canvassing and statistical studies. This processing is carried out within the framework of the execution of the general terms and conditions of sale. You have the right to access, rectify, limit and delete data concerning you, as well as the right to portability of your data, and the right to set guidelines regarding the retention, erasure, and disclosure of your personal data after your death. You also have the right to lodge a complaint to the CNIL (National committee of Information technology and freedoms) for any failure on our behalf to comply with the regulations in force. In addition, you have the right to object to commercial prospecting. You may exercise these rights, at any time, by sending your request to the following address: autobiz, 4 Place des Vosges, Immeuble Lavoisier, 92400 Courbevoie, France, or directly by e-mail to the autobiz data protection officer: dpo.autobiztrade@autobiz.com.
